<p source="SHANGBO.LANFU 8.51.1 (STRIP 1) MACHENGYUAN 8: 251 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-1a.1">[...] 旱,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-1a.2">雨露不降矣.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-1a.3">日月失時,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-1a.4">稊稗茂豐.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-1a.5">決去選物,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-1a.6">宅在幽中.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.LANFU 8.51.2 (STRIP 2) MACHENGYUAN 8: 254 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-2a.1">[...] 旱其不雨兮,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-2a.2">湫 (?)而不涸.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-2a.3">備修庶戒,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-2a.4">逢時焉作.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.LANFU 8.51.3 (STRIP 2) MACHENGYUAN 8: 259 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-3a.1">緩哉蘭兮!</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-3a.2">[...] 搖落</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-3a.3">而猶不失厥芳,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-3a.4">芳盈(=馨)蕊(謐, 蔥)彌(?)</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-3a.5">而達聞于四方.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-3a.6">處宅幽麓 [...]</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.LANFU 8.51.4 (STRIP 3) MACHENGYUAN 8: 259 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-4a.1">[...] 殘賊.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-4a.2">螻蟻虺蛇,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-4a.3">親眾秉志.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-4a.4">違遠行道,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-4a.5">不窮(?)有折,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-4a.6">蘭斯秉德,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-4a.7">取 [...]</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.LANFU 8.51.4 (STRIP 3) MACHENGYUAN 8: 259 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-5a.1">[...] 殘賊.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-5a.2">螻蟻虺蛇,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-5a.3">親眾秉志.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-5a.4">違遠行道,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-5a.5">不窮(?)有折,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-5a.6">蘭斯秉德,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-5a.7">取 [...]</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.LANFU 8.51.5 (STRIPS 4-5) MACHENGYUAN 8: 261 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-6a.1">[...] 年前其約儉,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-6a.2">美後其不長.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-6a.3">如蘭之不芳,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-6a.4">信蘭其沫 (? )也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-6a.5">風旱之不亡 (罔?),</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-6a.6">天道其越也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-6a.7">稊稗之方起,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0079_tls_001-6a.8">夫亦適其歲也.</seg>
                </p>

